'''Michael Sutfin''' is an illustrator who has created cover art for a number of books in the ''[[Star Wars Workbooks]]'' series, published by [[Workman Publishing]].<ref name="Preschool" /> Sutfin provided illustrations for ''[[The New Essential Guide to Characters]]''. He also drew the covers for ''[[Star Wars—Free Comic Book Day 2005 Special]]'' and [[Empire 35|''A Model Officer'']].

